 or property from loss, theft, or damages; and</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-117" dnum="b-o" numlevel="1" lineno="117" slineno="1-97" level="2"><display>(b)</display><amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="521" groupid="422" style="2" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" deltag="both">otherwise </amend><amendoutend style="2"/>comply with the general duties and responsibilities of a fiduciary or <ln numlevel="1" lineno="118" slineno="1-98"/>bailee.</subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-118" dnum="7-o" numlevel="1" lineno="119" slineno="1-99" level="1" space="false"><display>(7)</display><subsection ssid="1-null-119" dnum="a-o" level="2" placement="sameline"><display>(a)</display>A check from the trust account described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="31A-23a-406(2)(d)">(2)(d)</xref> may not be drawn, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="120" slineno="1-100"/>executed, or dated, or money otherwise disbursed unless the segregated trust account <ln numlevel="1" lineno="121" slineno="1-101"/>from which money is to be disbursed contains a sufficient credit balance consisting of <ln numlevel="1" lineno="122" slineno="1-102"/>collected and cleared money at the time the check is drawn, executed, or dated, or <ln numlevel="1" lineno="123" slineno="1-103"/>money is otherwise disbursed.</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-120" dnum="b-o" numlevel="1" lineno="124" slineno="1-104" level="2"><display>(b)</display>As used in this Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="31A-23a-406(7)">(7)</xref>, money is considered to be "collected and cleared," <ln numlevel="1" lineno="125" slineno="1-105"/>and may be disbursed as follows:<subsection ssid="1-null-121" dnum="i-o" numlevel="1" lineno="126" slineno="1-106" level="3"><display>(i)</display>cash may be disbursed on the same day the cash is deposited;</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-122" dnum="ii-o" numlevel="1" lineno="127" slineno="1-107" level="3"><display>(ii)</display>a wire transfer may be dis